OL,4,Crejected twice before ending
OL,5,Cindustrial action
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers' Council
OL,8,F(NITC), which represents the five main
OL,9,Funions in the sector, accepted the
OL,10,F5.5% pay offer, ending ongoing
OL,11,Findustrial action.
OL,13,FTeachers had rejected previous offers
OL,14,Famid concerns over workload, and had
OL,15,Fbeen taking part in industrial action
OL,16,Fshort of strike action.
OL,18,FSome of the unions had also voted in
OL,19,FDecember for strike action as part of
OL,20,Fthe ongoing dispute.
