OL,3,CTeachers accept pay offer they
OL,4,Crejected twice before ending
OL,5,Cindustrial action
OL,7,FThe unions said there had now been a
OL,8,Fpersonal intervention by Education
OL,9,FMinister Paul Givan to address their
OL,10,Fconcerns.
OL,12,FAn independent review to cover all
OL,13,Faspects of workload has been
OL,14,Fcommissioned.
OL,16,FMr Givan said the end of industrial
OL,17,Faction "will increase stability in our
OL,18,Fschools".
