OL,7,FHe added: "The pay settlement will see
OL,8,Fthe starting salary for graduate
OL,9,Fteachers increasing to #31,650.
OL,11,F"This is an increase of #1,650 over
OL,12,Fthe year and it follows on from the
OL,13,Fteachers' pay settlement in April 2024
OL,14,Fwhich saw the starting salary for
OL,15,Fteachers raised by almost 25%.
OL,17,F"New teachers are now being paid
OL,18,F#7,513 more than the salary paid prior
OL,19,Fto the Executive returning last year."
