OL,7,FIt is anticipated that the pay
OL,8,Fincrease will be applied to most
OL,9,Fteachers in May and a full-time
OL,10,Fteacher on the starting salary would
OL,11,Freceive #1,237.50 in back pay for the
OL,12,Fperiod from September 1 2024 to May 31
OL,13,F2025, while a full-time teacher on
OL,14,Fupper pay scale point 3 would receive
OL,15,F#1,913.25.
OL,17,FMr Givan added: "Constructive
OL,18,Fnegotiations have taken place with
OL,19,Ftrade unions and I have listened to
OL,20,Ftheir concerns about workload.
