OL,7,F"I want to make meaningful progress on
OL,8,Fthe issues to ensure that teachers
OL,9,Fhave the time and space to focus on
OL,10,Fwhat matters most ` teaching, learning
OL,11,Fand supporting pupils in the classroom.
OL,13,F"In order to seek to break the
OL,14,Fdeadlock, I proposed a commission to
OL,15,Fconduct an independent review of all
OL,16,Faspects of workload, that will be
OL,17,Ftaken forward by a three-member panel,
OL,18,Fcomprising an independent chair
OL,19,Fappointed by me, a member nominated by
OL,20,Fthe unions and a member nominated by
OL,21,Fmanagement side.
