OL,7,F"The panel will examine workload and
OL,8,Freport to me by the end of November."
OL,10,FJacquie White, the chairwoman of NITC
OL,11,Fsaid it was a "significant first step"
OL,12,Fin delivering tangible change for the
OL,13,Fteaching profession.
OL,15,FShe added: "All parties involved ` the
OL,16,Fminister, the employers and the
OL,17,Fteaching unions ` are now committed to
OL,18,Faddressing the concerns which have
OL,19,Fbeen raised by teachers and school
OL,20,Fleaders over a considerable period of
OL,21,Ftime.
